VALUES
  ('elementary-acfc4025-moex-00921', 'elementary-acfc4025', 'elementary-acfc4025-moex-110-01c5eaab', 'sub-elementary-acfc4025-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '詩人馬佛：「當青春在你的容顏留駐如朝露」、「以歡樂衝決生命一扇扇的鐵門」，所以人生應及時行樂。 下列詩句，何者符合馬佛所說的意思？', '["不如飲美酒，被服紈與素", "人生得意須盡歡，莫使金樽空對月", "枝在牆東花在西，自從落地任風吹", "閒雲潭影日悠悠，物換星移幾度秋 多情自古傷離別，更那堪，冷落清秋節"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:29:29+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "983a9bc5fc3b", "answer_pdf_sha1": "35b7bb1ab497", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110010", "c": "515", "s": "0101", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "國文(包括公文格式用語)", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 42, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "電子工程"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-acfc4025-moex-00922', 'elementary-acfc4025', 'elementary-acfc4025-moex-110-01c5eaab', 'sub-elementary-acfc4025-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '「四大讀書信念：第一條，要讀喜歡的書；第二條，要讀不喜歡的書；第三條，要在書中讀到自己，反思自 我；第四條，讀書不能替代行動，書裡是二手的人生，去工作、去戀愛、去旅行，真實認真活著，永遠活在 live現場轉播狀態，那才是一手的人生。」下列選項符合上文意旨的是：', '["讀書忌死讀", "讀書貴多不貴精", "盡信書不如無書", "讀萬卷書，行萬里路 讀書破萬卷，下筆如有神"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:29:29+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "983a9bc5fc3b", "answer_pdf_sha1": "35b7bb1ab497", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110010", "c": "515", "s": "0101", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "國文(包括公文格式用語)", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 43, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "電子工程"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-acfc4025-moex-00923', 'elementary-acfc4025', 'elementary-acfc4025-moex-110-01c5eaab', 'sub-elementary-acfc4025-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列「」內的動物，何者在成語中含有「人品性格」的象徵意義？', '["塞翁失「馬」", "驚弓之「鳥」", "「鶴」立雞群", "「狐」群狗黨 引「狼」入室"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:29:29+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "983a9bc5fc3b", "answer_pdf_sha1": "35b7bb1ab497", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110010", "c": "515", "s": "0101", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "國文(包括公文格式用語)", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 44, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "電子工程"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-acfc4025-moex-00924', 'elementary-acfc4025', 'elementary-acfc4025-moex-110-01c5eaab', 'sub-elementary-acfc4025-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '「繁華擾攘的羅東鎮，藏著一條名為『浮崙巷』的小徑，巷名充滿文藝感。名稱取自於當地舊名『浮崙仔』， 由於該區地勢高，水患淹不到，遠看像是浮出水面的車輪而得名。隨著街區發展更迭，周邊發展出夜市和商 圈，浮崙巷『鬧中取靜』，只有在地人知道的捷徑，獨樹一格成為文藝風小巷。在地文史工作者說，浮崙巷 正是在地鄉土作家黃春明出生地，早期著作《鑼》便是起源於此。」 這則報導從那幾個面向介紹「浮崙巷」？', '["地名由來", "特產小吃", "街巷特色", "著名地標 在地名人"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:29:29+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "983a9bc5fc3b", "answer_pdf_sha1": "35b7bb1ab497", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110010", "c": "515", "s": "0101", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "國文(包括公文格式用語)", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 45, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "電子工程"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-acfc4025-moex-00925', 'elementary-acfc4025', 'elementary-acfc4025-moex-110-35395ec3', 'sub-elementary-acfc4025-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '半徑為1毫米，長度為10公尺的銅線，其電阻係數為1.72×10-8歐姆‧公尺，該電阻值為何？', '["0.055 歐姆", "0.075 歐姆", "0.095 歐姆", "0.115 歐姆"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:29:29+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "822b349b9b10", "answer_pdf_sha1": "ae0b3bbd27f2", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110010", "c": "515", "s": "0703", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "基本電學大意", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 1, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "電子工程"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-acfc4025-moex-00926', 'elementary-acfc4025', 'elementary-acfc4025-moex-110-35395ec3', 'sub-elementary-acfc4025-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '如圖所示的電路，a、b兩端所看到的等效電阻R 為何？ ab', '["6 Ω", "8 Ω", "10 Ω", "12 Ω"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:29:29+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "822b349b9b10", "answer_pdf_sha1": "ae0b3bbd27f2", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110010", "c": "515", "s": "0703", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "基本電學大意", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 2, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "電子工程"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-acfc4025-moex-00927', 'elementary-acfc4025', 'elementary-acfc4025-moex-110-35395ec3', 'sub-elementary-acfc4025-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '有一2000瓦特的電熱水器，使用1小時，共消耗多少電能？', '["33.3J", "2kJ", "120kJ", "7.2MJ"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:29:29+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "822b349b9b10", "answer_pdf_sha1": "ae0b3bbd27f2", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110010", "c": "515", "s": "0703", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "基本電學大意", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 3, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "電子工程"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-acfc4025-moex-00928', 'elementary-acfc4025', 'elementary-acfc4025-moex-110-35395ec3', 'sub-elementary-acfc4025-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '以相同材料製作之a、b兩導線，若a的截面積為b的4倍，a的長度為b的6倍，則a導線與b導 線電阻值之比為何？', '["1：2", "2：3", "3：2", "4：1"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:29:29+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "822b349b9b10", "answer_pdf_sha1": "ae0b3bbd27f2", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110010", "c": "515", "s": "0703", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "基本電學大意", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 4, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "電子工程"}'::jsonb, NULL),
